snippet.title: v7.9 Stars Derailed Trailer — Honkai Impact 3rd x Honkai: Star Rail - Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
Honkai Impact 3rd x Honkai: Star Rail v7.9 Stars Derailed coming soon! Sparkle's new S-rank battlesuit Thousand-Faced Maestro: Cameo! debuts!
The crossover featured event Honkai: A Fool's Hand, Part 2 Main Story Chapter VI: Wails Stifled by the Silent Shadow, and other spectacular content await! Stay tuned!

Voice Artists:
Coralie 6626 Planck: Saya Aizawa
Litost: Kenji Hamada
